        <p>Question, "That this House do now adjourn until Tuesday, 21st May," put, and agreed to.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5CV0360P0-05327'>
        <a class='permalink' href='his-majestys-government-1#S5CV0360P0_19400513_HOC_71' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Resolved,
        <q>That this House welcomes the formation of a Government representing the united and inflexible resolve of the nation to prosecute the war with Germany to a victorious conclusion.</q>
      </p>
